gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Magic 103, Bulls 97
gameRecap.excerpt: The Magic defeated the Bulls, 103-97, and improve to 7-5 on the year and 1-1 in East Group C play. Franz Wagner led Orlando with 21 points and four rebounds as Jonathan Isaac totaled 18 points and nine rebounds. The Bulls were led by Zach LaVine (34 points, six rebounds) and DeMar DeRozan (23 points, four rebounds, and three assists). The Bulls move to 4-9 on the year and 0-2 in East Group C play.
